examples.en: The drug should be taken orally.

examples.en: The statement may be given orally or in writing.

examples.en: She practices good oral hygiene by brushing her teeth at least twice a day.

examples.en: As part of her oral examination, she had to recite the names of all the presidents.
examples.ru: В рамках устного экзамена ей пришлось перечислить имена всех президентов.

examples.en: He was administered the drug orally.
